Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:32.82,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(745,658)}も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:32.82,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1000,658)}もも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「揚帆濟滄海 極」的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:35.07,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(590,658)}わたのはら　こ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為「揚帆濟滄海 島」還在 保險起見要用圍手
